title: RimWorld v0.0.250 Pre-Alpha (All Platforms)
description:
Hey guys, I found the RimWorld v0.0.250 build on the internet after some searching. I tested it, and it works well.

It is not from the official source, so be aware! This may possibly harm your computer in some way, however I feel this is completely legitemate. 

This pack contains RimWorld build 250 for all three major platforms: Windows, Linux and Mac.

Have fun and keep 'em boomrats out!
